{
  "2317010": {
    "name": "Periculum",
    "steam_appid": 2317010,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/e52c1a1aaf8f0552d68aecb881ed1b44.avif?t=1728213424\" width=600 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Periculum</strong>是一款休闲（回合制和实时）战略游戏，你要征服六角形瓷砖并在上面建立你的帝国。收集资源、建造建筑和竖立城墙以加强你的帝国。从不同的游戏模式中选择，参加与机器人的史诗般的战斗，或挑战你的朋友，看谁最终获胜。有了广泛的选择，可能性是无穷的。在许多不同的地图上玩，或在关卡编辑器中创建自己的地图。游戏很容易学习，但通过可定制的设置，它也可以提供一个具有挑战性的经验。可在电脑（用鼠标和键盘）或虚拟现实（用运动控制器通过VR眼镜）上玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/291bbc6a0888211cd73c689e96a1e553.poster.avif?t=1728213424\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/291bbc6a0888211cd73c689e96a1e553.webm?t=1728213424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/291bbc6a0888211cd73c689e96a1e553.mp4?t=1728213424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8位玩家（多人游戏）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以和最多7个其他玩家或机器人一起玩。在线或本地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从8种颜色中选择一种，甚至可能与一些朋友或机器人组队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你和你的朋友也可以在你自己定制的关卡/地图上玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/c06d8b06020f98a82a5cf901d3197905.poster.avif?t=1728213424\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/c06d8b06020f98a82a5cf901d3197905.webm?t=1728213424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/c06d8b06020f98a82a5cf901d3197905.mp4?t=1728213424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超过7种游戏模式可供选择：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >默认。征服所有六边形并与其他玩家战斗。最后剩下六边形的玩家赢得游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夺旗。夺取敌人的旗帜，但不要失去自己的旗帜，否则将失去游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >山丘之王。在规定的时间内占领并保卫中心的六边形即可获胜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经济。成为第一个收集到指定数量资源的玩家（在黄金、木材、石头或鱼之间选择）。<br>[征服：第一个征服规定数量的六角形的玩家获胜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >弑君。每个玩家开始时都有一个国王，他可以四处移动，但如果国王丢失，游戏也会丢失。最后一个拥有国王的玩家将获胜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大逃杀。有或没有战利品散落在地图上供玩家收集。地图随着时间的推移不断缩小，直到只剩下一个六边形。谁拥有最后一个六边形，谁就赢得游戏。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/ff5822fe3150144d9990c8402d3a15a1.poster.avif?t=1728213424\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/ff5822fe3150144d9990c8402d3a15a1.webm?t=1728213424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/ff5822fe3150144d9990c8402d3a15a1.mp4?t=1728213424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义和关卡编辑器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用关卡编辑器建立你自己的自定义关卡/地图，并与你的朋友分享。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过许多选项来定制你的游戏，以满足你的喜好。例如，你可以调整部队的限制和地图的可见性（整个地图是否可见或必须先发现）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/d4fc90033fa1d9b35d0333c0fce6e6e0.poster.avif?t=1728213424\" width=460 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/d4fc90033fa1d9b35d0333c0fce6e6e0.webm?t=1728213424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/d4fc90033fa1d9b35d0333c0fce6e6e0.mp4?t=1728213424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建筑 </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大学：为你的军队解锁令人兴奋的升级，如更多的伤害或盔甲。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >市场：与其他玩家交易你收集的资源。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >房屋：可容纳5个居民，让你再训练5个部队。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >木墙：可用于防御。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >石墙：强度是木墙的两倍。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/0a16aee42f20c086c96f90d0f59376c8.poster.avif?t=1728213424\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/0a16aee42f20c086c96f90d0f59376c8.webm?t=1728213424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/0a16aee42f20c086c96f90d0f59376c8.mp4?t=1728213424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >士兵类型：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >步兵。标准</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >骑兵：双倍价格，双倍伤害，双倍健康，可以走两倍的路。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >弓箭手：可以攻击 1 格外的单位，造成标准伤害。 拥有双重健康。只能走标准距离，但可以通过大学升级为骑兵弓箭手。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大炮：对建筑物或其他部队造成大量的伤害。可以击中 2 个六边形半径内的目标。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(船舶计划在未来)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317010/extras/ce4cbeb606576f56d726534fbb0c43cf.avif?t=1728213424\" width=600 height=438 /></span></p>",
